  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast will be served in the hotels new breakfast room.</p>
<p>On Half Board, dinner will be a three course meal at the nearby La Grangia restaurant, just a short walk from the hotel. La Grangia has a really homely atmosphere and serves delicious Italian food; ideal after an active day on the slopes. It also has one of the biggest wine collections in the Alps!</p>
<p>The hotel has a lovely terrace which is a great place to have a drink and relax.</p>
<p>New Year Gala dinner included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
